scenes.description: Cecilia Immergreen performs the song 'Baraoku Otome' while dancing on a large clock-faced stage.
Cecilia finishes her performance, talks about the emotion 'Obsessiveness', and attempts to fight an overgrown Otomo mascot for justice before leading the viewer away.
A 'Now Loading...' screen featuring Cecilia playing maracas in various poses.
Cecilia wakes up on a new idol stage with a burning car behind her, expressing excitement at the new setting.
